# Privacy Policy  

**Effective Date:** 15/02/2025  

Thank you for using Bible for all. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.  

📌 Information We Collect
Our app does not collect or store personal data. However, we use Google AdMob, which may collect data for advertising and analytics.

👉 Collected by AdMob (Google):

Device Information (e.g., IP address, device type)
Advertising ID (IDFA) (used for ad tracking if permitted by user)
Usage Data (ad interactions, frequency of use)
📌 You can opt out of personalized ads via your device settings:

iOS: Settings → Privacy & Security → Tracking → Disable “Allow Apps to Request to Track.”
📌 Why We Collect This Information
We use Google AdMob to serve advertisements and:
✔️ Provide contextual ads based on app usage.
✔️ Improve ad relevance (if tracking is enabled).
✔️ Support app maintenance and development through ad revenue.

We do not:
❌ Store any personal data on our servers.
❌ Sell or share your personal data for third-party marketing.

📌 Third-Party Services & Tracking
We integrate Google AdMob, which may collect user data for advertising.

👉 Google AdMob Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

👉 How to Opt Out of Tracking: https://support.google.com/ads/answer/2662922?hl=en

📌 Digital Services Act (DSA) Compliance
If you are in the European Union (EU), we comply with the Digital Services Act (DSA) by:
✔️ Providing transparency on how ads are served.
✔️ Allowing users to control tracking preferences.
✔️ Giving you options to disable tracking & personalized ads.

📌 Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted in the app or on our website.

📌 Contact Us
If you have any questions or privacy concerns, feel free to contact us at:
📧 developer.queenbee@gmail.com
